{"tid":1243805,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那會唔會係2047前搞鳩香港經濟？？","createTime":"2019-06-19T15:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T16:11:31.000Z","uid":148187,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"db555e89c8313c097f3191bb26f9abfbddf1914b","tid":1243805,"uid":148187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:23:33.000Z","msg":"香港人而家咁唔聽話，係因為經濟未算差，如果香港經濟差就一定冇嘈嘅本錢。<br />\n香港回歸 Timeline:<br />\n1982 中英談判 -&gt; 1984 中英聯合聲明 -&gt; 1997 回歸<br />\n之前有巴打話香港前途根據以上timeline由公佈到落實大約13年時間，姐係2034，咁理論上中港談判就會係2032年前後。<br />\n支那近年經濟發達，慢慢減少經濟上對香港嘅依賴，過多幾年有毛有翼就絕對有能力搞鳩香港。<br />\n可能支那會喺2032年前幾年開始搞鳩香港，再畀啲小恩小惠吸引輿論傾向親中，營造大幅度歸化香港嘅條件，令香港人喺談判桌上甘願以自由換取經濟安定。<br />\n所以我地而家要減少經濟上對支那嘅依賴，以免將未來談判嘅籌碼先行送畀對方。<br />\n短期：唔淘寶唔返大陸玩唔用支那寶呢啲唔洗講<br />\n長期：公司以後盡量唔好同支那有往來 轉而投資東南亞 由企業層面學侵侵嗰套打擊支那"},{"pid":"8dc3f3e169f0c911d16f3e7987ca1d969a28de84","tid":1243805,"uid":148187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:24:39.000Z","msg":"陰謀論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981f4365f8d7bdcee7d06122d7b33215e79b158e","tid":1243805,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:25:14.000Z","msg":"無咁長命啦"},{"pid":"d869e9e51902bb641c162de8814eca0f508bc4c7","tid":1243805,"uid":148187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:26:41.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b1b6f0cbc8a63422e1e4cdd7e54a0a73b0df28","tid":1243805,"uid":148187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dfb03998db31a3b6d3f585089d4003af3798c61","tid":1243805,"uid":35341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"